01:07:27.496 --> 01:07:30.841
LIAM: That is-- these dice-- That's a 17.

01:07:30.841 --> 01:07:32.232
MATT: Cool. That's one success.

01:07:32.232 --> 01:07:32.848
LIAM: Yeah.

01:07:32.848 --> 01:07:33.889
MATT: All right.

01:07:33.889 --> 01:07:35.393
SAM: Deez dice.

01:07:35.393 --> 01:07:38.496
MATT: At the end of Vera's turn, this goes away.

01:07:38.496 --> 01:07:41.397
MARISHA and SAM: Oh.

01:07:41.397 --> 01:07:46.633
LAURA: Yeah, which sucks for us, and now they can
