01:07:46.633 --> 01:07:51.964
MATT: The sleet and stuff has now melted and
dripped off the sides. These guards here--

01:07:51.964 --> 01:07:55.402
LIAM: (guard impression) "What's all this, then?"

01:07:55.402 --> 01:08:06.306
MATT: (counting) 30 on each side, and they're both
