dogpile in to try to stop her from moving. We have

01:10:03.119 --> 01:10:04.639
three attempting to grapple you, Nott.

01:10:04.639 --> 01:10:05.485
SAM: Three?

01:10:05.485 --> 01:10:06.084
MATT: Yes.

01:10:06.084 --> 01:10:08.474
MARISHA: You're tiny. You're dexy.

01:10:08.474 --> 01:10:10.124
SAM: Sure, sure. Here we go.

01:10:10.124 --> 01:10:11.195
MARISHA: Slippy.

