MATT: That's a success. Next guy, natural 20.

01:10:22.024 --> 01:10:23.430
LAURA: Oh, no.

01:10:23.430 --> 01:10:24.358
MATT: That's 22.

01:10:24.358 --> 01:10:25.148
SAM: Natural 20.

01:10:25.148 --> 01:10:28.245
(surprised laughter)

01:10:28.245 --> 01:10:30.024
TALIESIN: What the fuck is happening?

