MATT: Seven points of damage.

01:13:39.103 --> 01:13:39.985
TRAVIS: Okay.

01:13:39.985 --> 01:13:42.713
MATT: The last one is 14 to hit.

01:13:42.713 --> 01:13:46.536
TRAVIS: Misses. Yeah, misses. Armor class 15.

